Some
people
break
promises
as
readily
as
they
make
them.
Some
people
break
promises
as
readily
as
they
make
them.
As
a
result,
they
acquire
a
reputation
for
unreliability.
It
is
particularly
important
to
be
reliable
in
the
business
world.
A
person
or
firm
that
comes
to
be
regarded
as
unreliable
has
a
poor
chance
of
success.
